            <title>[LU-17646] lustreapi: add FID in error messages </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17646</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;llapi_lease_set(), llapi_lease_check() and other functions when report an error do not provide specific FID of failed file.&#160; Use llapi_fd2fid(fd) to get lu_fid (if possible).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the getting the FID fails, still report an error message in the old style without FID&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
